<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="welcome-vt">welcome <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'welkəm/    美 /'welkəm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-greet">1.★ <strong>欢迎；迎接 (greet)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Ladies and gentlemen, let’s welcome Jane Carter. 
女士们，先生们，让我们欢迎简·卡特。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>愉快地接受：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We would especially welcome articles about how Americans spend their holidays and festivals.
我们特别欢迎有关美国人是如何度过节假日的文章。</p><footer>2015 全国书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ll welcome any suggestions.
任何建议我都会欣然接受。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Brown stood at the door, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (欢迎) newcomers with a large smile.  （2009 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. welcoming  </p></div>